    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1479500/extras/7e7c18eebd4ce2fd6e9aaad6ae550142.avif?t=1762274991\" width=600 height=336 /></span><br><br>《湛蓝牢笼》为多结局的2D日式文字冒险游戏。<br>由知名轻小说家撰写，共二十五万字的完全原创剧本及保证烧脑的剧情！<br>再搭配近20首原创配乐，与名歌手演唱的专属主题曲，<br>及名绘师玉莳良操刀的丰富图像及超精致立绘演出！<br>融合推理、悬疑、恋爱、科幻等要素，让玩家展开一场高度沉浸的海底列车救赎之旅。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1479500/extras/b2c61713ce835d4032f017b112b7629b.poster.avif?t=1762274991\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1479500/extras/b2c61713ce835d4032f017b112b7629b.webm?t=1762274991\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1479500/extras/b2c61713ce835d4032f017b112b7629b.mp4?t=1762274991\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >▌故事｜Story</h2><strong>深海下无尽的血腥轮回，你能为众人带来救赎吗？</strong><br>穿梭海底的列车，载满欢度毕业旅行的学生，却困在噩梦般的时间轮回，无止尽地重复列车出轨意外发生的时刻……<br><br>玩家扮演喜欢列车的男高中生吾时，<br>与好友、青梅竹马及上百位同学，<br>一同参加由大财团＂铯＂家千金主办的海底列车豪华之旅。<br>然而，出轨意外、隧道破裂、海水灌入导致的溺毙与谋杀......<br><br>不时闪过脑海中的绝望画面，<br>一步步带领玩家解开关于这场旅行、及这辆列车的残酷真相──<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1479500/extras/8390c8e269084041fce6c0bafc3904c9.poster.avif?t=1762274991\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1479500/extras/8390c8e269084041fce6c0bafc3904c9.webm?t=1762274991\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1479500/extras/8390c8e269084041fce6c0bafc3904c9.mp4?t=1762274991\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >▌人物介绍｜Characters</h2><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1479500/extras/6f7253b9cdc4dbbf8a48230a5dc30584.avif?t=1762274991\" width=482 height=224 /></span><br>本作男主角。<br>热爱铁路及列车，尤其是划时代的海底宽轨观光列车＂时之旅＂。<br>性格直来直往，朋友多达两人，与姮笙、宇光从小一同长大，不管发生什么事都一起面对。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1479500/extras/c5e181388a70830644ac89e6bd926609.avif?t=1762274991\" width=482 height=224 /></span><br>吾时的青梅竹马，充满邻家女孩气息的存在。<br>看到名牌和高价品会双眼放光，但实际上比所有人都还勤俭持家，梦想是建立一个美满且平凡的家庭。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1479500/extras/9b3d1f00cd89ce2d5c28a8241884edea.avif?t=1762274991\" width=482 height=224 /></span><br>大财团＂铯＂＂的唯一继承人，也是本次毕业旅行的主办者。<br>能文能武，才貌双全，但在完美的外表下，似乎隐藏着不为人知的一面。<br>校内谣传她正在进行某种用人类做为材料的恐怖实验。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1479500/extras/a0d384e0812e39eae1a85b532eae2aaf.avif?t=1762274991\" width=482 height=224 /></span><br>铯月大小姐的专属女仆，也是小吾时、宇光、姮笙一届的学妹。<br>能为铯月做任何事，甚至牺牲性命也在所不惜。似乎曾遭遇过什么特殊经历，使她脸上永远带着淡淡的笑容。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1479500/extras/71261e3f540dd999fa4e2941039acca7.avif?t=1762274991\" width=482 height=224 /></span><br>吾时、姮笙的共同好友。校内篮球队的主力球员，体格健壮，然而女人缘似乎普普。<br>一路走来对吾时与姮笙微妙的相处模式抱持疑惑，半是担心、半是无奈地守护着两人。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1479500/extras/87ce435e7494bb5f204d9d71e753da5d.poster.avif?t=1762274991\" width=482 height=225 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1479500/extras/87ce435e7494bb5f204d9d71e753da5d.webm?t=